<title>USA: Harvard Industries names Adams chairman.</title>
<headline>Harvard Industries names Adams chairman.</headline>
<dateline>TAMPA, Fla. 1997-02-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harvard Industries said it has named John Adams as its chairman and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>The company also named Roger Burtraw as president.</p>
<p>Earlier, Harvard reported a first quarter loss of $4.90 per share compared with a loss of $0.78 a year earlier.</p>
